ef=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ghp1665702680667.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ghp1665702680667.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ghp1665702680667.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ghp1665702680667\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Clear the memory that was allocated for sending the mail.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ghp1665702680667__topic_d133847e1_d133848e1_d133849e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ghp1665702680667__p_d133850e1_d133851e1_d133852e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ClearMail</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ghp1665702680667__section_shh_3gz_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1174313e64\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ghp1665702680667__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in $status</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ghp1665702680667__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ghp1665702680667__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ghp1665702680667__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ghp1665702680667__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">Operation succeeded</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ghp1665702680667__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">-18</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ghp1665702680667__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">Memory allocation error</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ghp1665702680667__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">&lt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ghp1665702680667__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">An error occurred</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ghp1665702680667__section_ztv_jgz_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1174313e125\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">When sending email, Uniface maintains the complete message structure, including header\n        information, message body, attachments, inline objects in memory, and information retrieved\n        via <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">GetRecipientDetails</span>. To clear this memory, call the\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ClearMail</span> operation or delete the UPOPMAIL component instance, which\n        implicitly clears the memory.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ghp1665702680667_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ghp1665702680667__codeblock_rn4_kgz_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables\n handle mailApiHandle\nendvariables\n\n; create the instance handle\nnewinstance \"UPOPMAIL\", mailApiHandle\n\n&lt;snip&gt;log on to server, set message header and content, send mail, then log off mail server &lt;/snip&gt;\n\n; clear the mail message structure\nmailApiHandle-&gt;ClearMail()</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kae1665702681104.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>GetRecipientDetails</a><p>Get the response code and message from the SMTP server for each recipient that was not accepted during the last Send() operation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527854\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527854\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ClearMail Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Clear the memory that was allocated for sending the mail. ClearMail ( ) Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $status Value Description 0 Operation succeeded -18 Memory allocation error <0 An error occurred Description When sending email, Uniface maintains the complete message structure, including header information, message body, attachments, inline objects in memory, and information retrieved via GetRecipientDetails . To clear this memory, call the ClearMail operation or delete the UPOPMAIL component instance, which implicitly clears the memory. Explain this code variables handle mailApiHandle endvariables ; create the instance handle newinstance \"UPOPMAIL\", mailApiHandle <snip>log on to server, set message header and content, send mail, then log off mail server </snip> ; clear the mail message structure mailApiHandle->ClearMail() Copy Related Links GetRecipientDetails Get the response code and message from the SMTP server for each recipient that was not accepted during the last Send() operation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}